# Battery Monitor 2.0 for Hubitat

**Author:** Jdthomas24  
**Namespace:** jdthomas24  
**Version:** 2.0  

## Description
Advanced Hubitat battery monitoring with analytics, trends, and replacement tracking. Auto-discover devices, monitor battery health, track replacements, and receive daily reports.

## Installation
- Install via Hubitat Package Manager.
- Auto-discover battery devices and select which devices to monitor.
- Configure daily summary time and notifications.
- Monitor battery trends and replacement history.

## Notes
- Battery trends may be overestimated until at least 5 battery events have been reported.
- Auto discovery must be used to select which devices to monitor.
- Daily report sorts devices by Critical, Good, and Full categories for easy reading.
- Manual battery replacement can be tracked via the Replacement page.
